\begin_inset Formula $W$
\end_inset

) such that
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi^{\diamond}(v_{1}\otimes v_{2})=(\varphi v_{1})v_{2}\quad\text{and}\quad(\psi_{\diamond}v_{1})v_{2}=\psi(v_{1}\otimes v_{2})
\]

\end_inset

for all 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1},v_{2}\in V$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\in\mathrm{Hom}(V,\mathrm{Hom}(V,W))$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\in\mathrm{Hom}(V\otimes V,W)$
\end_inset

.
 We denote
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{D}^{2}f(u)=((\mathrm{D}(\mathrm{D}f))(u))^{\diamond}
\]

\end_inset

and think of 
