\begin_layout Plain Layout

Proposition~(
\backslash
ref{prop6.7})
\end_layout

\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\circ F\circ\phi^{-1}$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $C^{\infty}$
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi(p)$
\end_inset

.
 Since 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi(p)$
\end_inset

 was an arbitary point of 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi(U\cap F^{-1}(V))$
\end_inset

, the map 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\circ F\circ\phi^{-1}:\phi(U\cap F^{-1}(V))\to\mathbb{R}^{m}$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $C^{\infty}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

