begin{example}
\backslash
label{example}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 The morphism 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{A}^{1}\to\mathbb{A}^{1}$
\end_inset

 given by 
\begin_inset Formula $t\mapsto t^{2}$
\end_inset

 is not etale because it is ramified at 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

.
 Indeed,
\begin_inset Formula 
