\end_inset

 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $f\colon\mathbb{A}^{m}\to\mathbb{A}^{m}$
\end_inset

 be a morphism.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 is etale in a neighborhood of 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

